temporary hack to ensure at least some semblance of realism.  Made car 
reflections default to fully reflective (seems to make more sense than 
defaulting to fully non-reflective).  Added z-buffer offset to the 
blended objects (like the wear marks on the road) to fix the artifacts 
they had.


