------------------------------------------------------------------------
r1586 | thelusiv | 2007-03-05 02:44:31 -0800 (Mon, 05 Mar 2007) | 5 lines

Number of laps remaining for unfinished players now displayed with race results when single race is left before all players are done.
Unfinished players now sort correctly after all other players.
Added several new options: joystick.ff_invert flips the force feedback, control.speed_sens_steering controls how much speed affects steering limitation, joystick.two_hundred limits steering range to 200 degrees.
All these new options plus joystick.ff_gain (added but not commented on before, controls gain on force feedback), are now in the menus. All these options are hooked up in vamosworld.cc, but none have been tested yet.

