r1339 | thelusiv | 2006-11-12 00:21:04 -0800 (Sun, 12 Nov 2006) | 5 lines

More changes to automatic shifting:
* Downshifts happen at a slightly lower point than before
* If the car is in 2nd gear it will not down shift until below 2000 RPM
* Removed requirement for upshifting to only occur when RPM was increasing (fix missed upshift bug)

------------------------------------------------------------------------
