------------------------------------------------------------------------
r1311 | joevenzon | 2006-10-29 19:10:43 -0800 (Sun, 29 Oct 2006) | 3 lines

Disabled ABS below 6 kph.


------------------------------------------------------------------------
r1310 | joevenzon | 2006-10-29 19:08:45 -0800 (Sun, 29 Oct 2006) | 3 lines

Rewrote ABS (again).  This should be the last time I have to do it.


------------------------------------------------------------------------
r1309 | joevenzon | 2006-10-29 15:41:31 -0800 (Sun, 29 Oct 2006) | 7 lines

Fully implemented M Denny ABS algorithm from 
http://www.iop.org/EJ/article/0143-0807/26/6/008/ejp5_6_008.pdf

The only pitfall was that I had to estimate the wheel weight at 30 kg since the 
wheel->mass() function was returning zero.


------------------------------------------------------------------------
r1308 | joevenzon | 2006-10-29 14:33:52 -0800 (Sun, 29 Oct 2006) | 4 lines

Implemented correction to hopefully catch up when the client/host gets out of 
sync.


------------------------------------------------------------------------
r1307 | joevenzon | 2006-10-29 14:17:43 -0800 (Sun, 29 Oct 2006) | 3 lines

Removed texture debugging messages.


------------------------------------------------------------------------
r1306 | joevenzon | 2006-10-29 14:05:23 -0800 (Sun, 29 Oct 2006) | 3 lines

Eliminated redundant calls to SetReflectionTexture.  Removed ABS debug prints.


------------------------------------------------------------------------
r1305 | thelusiv | 2006-10-29 13:56:33 -0800 (Sun, 29 Oct 2006) | 2 lines

Setting car reflection texture in SpinningCar only once when the car is loaded, instead of every time it is drawn.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r1304 | thelusiv | 2006-10-29 13:34:33 -0800 (Sun, 29 Oct 2006) | 2 lines

Fixed some bugs causing textboxes not to get saved, meaning that a person couldn't connect to a server because it would ignore the value they put into the Server IP setting.

