r991 | thelusiv | 2006-05-03 20:53:58 -0700 (Wed, 03 May 2006) | 2 lines

The settings class now takes full advantage of the options.config file. All the available options are in there. In order to do this, some other classes' constructors had to be modified so that no settings were queried before the options file is parsed.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r990 | thelusiv | 2006-05-03 07:12:21 -0700 (Wed, 03 May 2006) | 2 lines

