r934 | thelusiv | 2006-04-18 23:37:49 -0700 (Tue, 18 Apr 2006) | 2 lines

Changed OK button press behavior so that if no changes are made to an options page in the menu (for instance, Display Options) the SaveSettings() function has no effect. This causes Display Options to no longer force a texture reload if the user presses OK but has made no changes.

