------------------------------------------------------------------------
r392 | joevenzon | 2005-10-09 11:43:40 -0700 (Sun, 09 Oct 2005) | 13 lines

I've added support for user-defined torque curves.  Just put something 
like

      <torque-curve friction="0.00025">
        [ 1000.0, 150.0 ]
        [ 2000.0, 200.0 ]
        [ 6000.0, 300.0 ]
        [ 8000.0 250.0 ]
      </torque-curve>

in the engine section.


------------------------------------------------------------------------
