r61 | thelusiv | 2005-08-02 21:54:47 -0700 (Tue, 02 Aug 2005) | 2 lines

Updated S2000 suspension once again: moved hinges, recalculated spring constants, and reduced rear bounce and rebound dampers. Eliminated some of the wobbling and improved turnability, but still not quite driftable.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
