r43 | joevenzon | 2005-07-30 11:48:15 -0700 (Sat, 30 Jul 2005) | 6 lines

The robustness of the replay system has been vastly improved.  Cars 
should be kept in sync with the recording and hopefully will work 
properly across computers.  This also lays the groundwork for 
networked multiplayer syncing.


