r13 | joevenzon | 2005-07-23 16:05:30 -0700 (Sat, 23 Jul 2005) | 4 lines

The tire friction model no longer barfs when going over bumps.  Note:  
the fix for this is kind of a hack, but it seems to work just fine.


------------------------------------------------------------------------
r12 | joevenzon | 2005-07-23 15:57:45 -0700 (Sat, 23 Jul 2005) | 5 lines

Used Beckman's combination grip formula from the Physics of Racing 
series.  The RWD vehicles finally behave correctly!  Also, fixed a 
loading screen bug and made it use the cleaner font.


------------------------------------------------------------------------
