planned improvements.


------------------------------------------------------------------------
r9 | thelusiv | 2005-07-23 11:29:12 -0700 (Sat, 23 Jul 2005) | 3 lines

Added more weight to the car, reduced engine weight, and moved the suspension hinges in an attempt to 
reduce understeer

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r8 | joevenzon | 2005-07-22 07:41:38 -0700 (Fri, 22 Jul 2005) | 5 lines

Added some sanity checks to tire friction forces, updated s2000.xml to 
use suspension and tire coefficients from an s2000 spoon made for Racer, 
and updated the mustang to use alpine's tire data.


------------------------------------------------------------------------
r7 | joevenzon | 2005-07-21 17:26:11 -0700 (Thu, 21 Jul 2005) | 5 lines

There are now separate models and textures for front/rear wheels.  The selected car is now 
stored more reliably.  The mustang is now running on some 16" all-season tires -- makes it 
much tougher to drive!


